data.eml:eml: A new tanaidacean subfamily, Bathytanaidinae (Crustacea: Paratanaididae), from the Australian continental shelf and slope

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Larsen, Kim, Heard, Richard W.
